{
  "texts": [
    "Algorithm 1 can easily incorporate drones with such cameras.",
    "The drone will have to additionally communicate the pitch and yaw of the gimbal to the regulatory authority.",
    "Using this information, the regulatory authority can calculate the angle (𝛼) between the drone's direction of motion and the camera's orientation.",
    "The angle 𝛼 can be applied as a corrective factor to 𝜙 on line 5.",
    "The same idea can also be applied to account for the yaw and pitch of the drone itself, and suitable corrective factors can be applied to 𝜙."
  ]
}